# --- Environment & secrets ---
# Never commit API keys, DB URLs, or LLM-provider keys.
# Blocks every dotenv variant at ANY depth in the repo, including
# `manual-testing/*/.env*` where developers keep local OPENAI_API_KEY,
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, GOOGLE_API_KEY, etc. Template files
# (`.env.example`, `.env.sample`, `.env.template`) stay allowed so a
# fresh contributor knows which vars to set.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.sample
!.env.template
# Common non-dotenv secret containers.
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets.json
credentials.json
service-account*.json

